            <h2>Mastering the Apex: Cornering Techniques</h2>
            <span class="post-meta">Posted on December 11, 2025 by Ace Driver</span>
            <p>Cornering is where you win or lose the race. The key is finding the *apex*—the innermost point of the corner. Brake early and in a straight line, turn in slightly before the corner's start, hit the apex, and then immediately accelerate out, letting the kart naturally drift to the outside edge of the track. This maximizes your exit speed, which is crucial for the following straightaway!</p>
            <p>Remember: Slow in, fast out!</p>
