            <p>New to karting? Welcome! For beginners, a **four-stroke (4-stroke)** engine is highly recommended. They are less complex, easier to maintain, and offer a more predictable power delivery compared to the high-revving two-strokes. Focus on learning the driving lines and throttle control before upgrading to a faster class.</p>
